    {
      "id": "title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -200,
      "y": -300,
      "width": 1700,
      "height": 150,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "# Specorator — UI Map (current & future state)\nViews · modals · panels and their responsibilities. **🟩 Green = ships today** · **🟦 Cyan = new in v1** · **🟥 Red = safety-critical**. Code symbols in `mono`. Companion to [[Specorator Architecture (C4)]]."
    },
    {
      "id": "legend",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1720,
      "y": -470,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 420,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## Legend\n\n**🟩 Green** — exists today (don't regress).\n**🟦 Cyan** — new surface for v1.\n**🟥 Red** — safety-critical.\n\n`Type`: View = dedicated pane (ItemView) · Modal = dialog · Panel/Card = lives inside a view.\n\nEdges: **opens / contains ▼ / extends**.\n\n*New surfaces follow the [[Quick Actions]] card model: tap to use, no files or JSON.*"
    },
    {
      "id": "entry_ribbon",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -120,
      "y": 120,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "**Ribbon + Command palette** 🟩\n*(entry points)*\nOpen chat · open board · inline edit · copy diagnostics · add file/folder to context."
    },
    {
      "id": "view_chat",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 220,
      "y": 100,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 170,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## Chat View 🟩\n`ClaudianView` — right-sidebar ItemView. The main conversation surface; hosts everything in the band below."
